headline: Humana Faces Medicare Setbacks But Bets Big On Long-Term Care Growth
summary: Humana Inc.'s shares up 21%, but it is facing near-term headwinds from Medicare Advantage ratings and profit outlook. Read why HUM stock is a Hold.
